Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:17.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Seems like only yesterday I was saving this place from being totally destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:19.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:25.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You only mentioned it about fifteen times on the train here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:29.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, and we never hear a peep out of you about your exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Point taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all wanted to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:35.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I  don't think it's gonna be that exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:39.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I pretty much just have to smile and wave as the dignitaries arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, but you get to smile and wave like a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How exactly is that different from smilin' and wavin' like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,not a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:53.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:57.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why the lo-o-o-o-o-o-o-ong face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:00.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've just been felling a little unsure about things lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:03.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem that my new role as a princess equates to all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's just silly. You got a real important role in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:11.38,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia wouldn't have asked you to come today if she didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of course we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:15.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now hurry along!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:18.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You don't want to risk having that important role diminished
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:20.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,because you're tardy for your regal meeting greet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:26.73,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Duke and Duchess of Maretonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,That was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:56.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia had you come all the way to the Crystal Empire just to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:01.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, wow, really regal and important, he-he.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:58.17,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Thank you for understanding our desire to keep the numbers of those privy to our confidential discussions to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else I can do to assist with their visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.90,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Twilight, but the visit is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.21,Luna,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess I just don't really understand why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Couldn't one of the Royal Guard have unfurled the banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.43,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Having all four of us in the Empire to greet them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:29.05,Celestia,,0,0,0,,lets the dignitaries know that their visit is considered an important one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.10,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Plus, it gives me an opportunity to see my favourite sister-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I'm happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:39.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But… ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that Princess Luna raises the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia raises the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you protect the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:52.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and all I seem to do is... smile and wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:08.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It isn't that I'm ungrateful\NFor all the things that I've earned
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:16.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,For all the journeys I have taken\NAll the lessons that I have learned
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:25.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I wonder where I'm going now\NWhat my role is meant to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:33.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to travel\NTo a future that I can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:46.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have my wings, I wear this crown\NI'm a princess, this is true
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:54.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it's still unclear to me\NJust what I am meant to do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:05:02.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I want to have a purpose\NWant to do all that I can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:11.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I want to make a contribution\NI want to be a part of the plan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:19.79,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Your destiny's uncertain\NAnd that's sometimes hard to take
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:27.49,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But it will become much clearer\NWith every new choice you make
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:34.81,Luna,,0,0,0,,Patience is never easy\NI understand wanting more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:42.65,Luna,,0,0,0,,I know how hard it is to wait\NTo spread out your wings and soar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:49.51,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,But you stand here for a reason\NYou're gifted and you are strong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:56.16,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,That crown is upon your head because\NYou belong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:03.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Know that your time is coming soon\NAs the sun rises, so does the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:12.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,As love finds a place in every heart\NYou are a princess, you'll play your part
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:19.19,Luna,,0,0,0,,We understand you wanting more\NA chance to shine, a chance to soar
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:25.74,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Soon will come the day it turns around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:32.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Know that your time is coming soon\NAs the sun rises, so does the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:44.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,As love finds a place in every heart\NYou are a princess, you'll play your part
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:52.69,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You are a princess, you'll play your part
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.71,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Your time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:27.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Very sorry, he-he, you came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:34.01,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Is he friend or is he foe, the pony wonders…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:39.13,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I can assure you, I am no friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.63,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I am Lord Tirek,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:48.32,Tirek,,0,0,0,,and I will take what should have been mine long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:11.69,Luna,,0,0,0,,Sister, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.27,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I've just had the most terrible dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.20,Luna,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.81,Luna,,0,0,0,,You know as well as I that this was not a dream but a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.59,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Then we haven't much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:26.03,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The stronger he becomes, the more we are all in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.50,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Tirek and his brother Scorpan came here from a distant land,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.46,Celestia,,0,0,0,,intent on stealing Equestrian magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:46.12,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But Scorpan soon came to appreciate the ways of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.79,Celestia,,0,0,0,,even befriending a young unicorn wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,Scorpan urged his brother to abandon their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.14,Luna,,0,0,0,,When Tirek refused, Scorpan alerted us to Tirek's intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Scorpan returned to his own land,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.94,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and Tirek was sent to Tartarus for his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.41,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But it appears he has found a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:09.47,Luna,,0,0,0,,We believe, it happened when Cerberus has left his post at the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But that was a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why is he just now starting to steal magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.52,Celestia,,0,0,0,,His time in Tartarus left him very weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:20.52,Celestia,,0,0,0,,He has just now gained enough strength to use his dark powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:23.89,Luna,,0,0,0,,But with each passing moment he grows stronger still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.72,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,And I know just the princess who can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.22,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll find him…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.89,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must call in another to stop Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.26,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,As in "Discord" Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's that big of a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He can be very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He can sense when there's a magical imbalance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:52.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The next time Tirek steals magic, Discord will be able to track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, what are you supposed to do in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Less, of course, one of you needs me to smile and wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,To the Castle of the Two Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not really needed anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Might as well catch up on some of my reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You want some company?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:16.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It has been a while since we've visited the Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Might be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could use a little company right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe we had to give back the Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It had to be done or the Tree of Harmony wouldn't have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But Twilight was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:36.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Even without the Elements, our friendship is as strong as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:41.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just hope another "friend" of ours never makes us sorry we had to give them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.83,Discord,,0,0,0,,You're talking about me, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How'd you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.83,Discord,,0,0,0,,My ears were burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are you even doing here, Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:57.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a bit of light reading before I head off on my extremely important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:02.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,I suppose you all know that I've been tasked to capture a certain escapee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:07.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike. It is a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:15.35,Discord,,0,0,0,,Seems I possess a magic that gives me quite an important role in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.92,Discord,,0,0,0,,Maybe they should make me an Alicorn princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,I never dream of such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.67,Discord,,0,0,0,,Ask Princess Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a creepy magic-stealin' villain to track down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.21,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's just that I couldn't help but notice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:43.92,Discord,,0,0,0,,that Twilight hasn't yet opened this little chest of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:48.39,Discord,,0,0,0,,It got me thinking: what if what's locked inside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.61,Discord,,0,0,0,,is something that could help her prove her royal worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.69,Discord,,0,0,0,,I only bring it up because she said that she's been feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:58.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,like her role as a princess doesn't equate to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,How do you know how she was feeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Is eavesdropping not the way you're supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,to find out what your best pals are up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, woe is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:14.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,Will I ever learn the intricate nuances of being a good friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.96,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well in any case, I suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:22.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,now is as good a time as any to make my exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And good riddance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.23,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oopsie-doopsie,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:32.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,I almost left with the little journal you've all been keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:37.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,What a fascinating read. Haven't you girls just learned so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:43.08,Discord,,0,0,0,,I've bookmarked a few more interesting passages you really should take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.73,Discord,,0,0,0,,We're still on for tea later, right, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:52.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll bring the cucumber sandwiches...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I think the 'reformed' Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:00.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,is more obnoxious than the before-he-was-reformed Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But he could be right, couldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:07.39,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What if there is something important in that chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:26.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There must be something in this library that can help me figure out how to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:30.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The answer's in one of these books, I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.59,Discord,,0,0,0,,Tirek, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.82,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.28,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You're free?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.19,Discord,,0,0,0,,As a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.91,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I commend you on your escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid the feeling isn't mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:20.78,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I should have known you would want to have Equestria all to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:24.26,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not doing this for me. I'm doing it for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:28.04,Discord,,0,0,0,,Just between the two of us, it's mostly for Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.34,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.90,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You're not saying you're friends with ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.77,Discord,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.60,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I am surprised that someone with your intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:45.11,Tirek,,0,0,0,,does not see this 'friendship' is but a new form of inprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:50.49,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Clearly you've had to abandon your true nature to stay in their good graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.85,Discord,,0,0,0,,I have done nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.59,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.96,Tirek,,0,0,0,,But he was always weak minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.03,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You are Discord, you are legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.97,Tirek,,0,0,0,,you cannot fall into the same trap that claimed my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:13.51,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Help me to grow strong, and be rewarded
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:17.23,Tirek,,0,0,0,,with something far greater than friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.64,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:24.75,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Once I've stripped these ponies of their magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.81,Tirek,,0,0,0,,nothing will give me greater pleasure than to see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.57,Tirek,,0,0,0,,their world turned upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:35.08,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Who better to do so than the master of chaos himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:41.43,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Join me, Discord, and reclaim your greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:45.67,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Unless, of course, 'pony errand-boy' is the role
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.42,Tirek,,0,0,0,,you've always wanted to play in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've been reading our journal, and there's something interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,about the sections Discord bookmarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack, do you remember when you had to tell everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that the tonic Granny bought from the Flim Flam brothers didn't really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It was one of the hardest things I ever had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I hate to disappoint everypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but there's no way Granny could have made that dive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,because this tonic is a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And in that moment, I knew I had to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:41.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But what's that got to do with openin' the chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:44.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've found that each of you has had to face a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:47.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,where living up to the Element of Harmony you represent wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:51.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, it was when you realized that the way to show kindness to the Breezies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:53.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,was by forcing them to leave their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, the looks on their poor little faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:03.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But I knew that was difficult as it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:06.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,pushing them away was the kindest thing I could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:11.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity, even after Suri took advantage of your generosity at Fashion Week in Manehattan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you didn't let it cause you to abandon your generous spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:17.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I simply couldn't have lived with myself\N if I didn't do something special for the friends
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,who have always been so generous to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:25.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, you had the chance to fly with the Wonderbolts at the Equestria Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But instead you chose to compete with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sure, but being loyal to my friends was way…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ooh! My turn, my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:35.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, you realised that seeing your friend laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:39.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,was more important than proving you were a better party planner than Cheese Sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Best party I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's clear we've all had our moments to shine, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But I'm with Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:49.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What does any of this have to do with the opening of the chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All of you had tough choices to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but when you made the right one and embraced your element,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It helped somepony else make the right choice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Each of you recieved something from the pony whose life you helped change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know it sounds crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:08.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but maybe there's something special about those objects that could lead us to the location of the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The chest is connected to the Tree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Tree is connected to the Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And the Elements are connected to all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There must be a connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:22.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but maybe Discord was trying to be a good friend after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything on them that would give us a clue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,as to where the keys might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They're just ordinary everyday objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Come on, Boneless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:34.51,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Give us a key!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's still one key missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The key that represents the Element of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My Element.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I'm sure that if we've gotten our keys,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,you have too, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:19.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Think, Twilight, when have you completed a difficult magical task,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and in doing so encouraged another pony to do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If I had I would've written about it in the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:30.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twilight, I'm sure you'll get your key eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That I'm needed in Canterlot at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I came as quickly as I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:49.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong? Is it Tirek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I put too much trust in Discord,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:54.86,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and the effect that friendship would have upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.86,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord have betrayed the ponies of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.05,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and joined forces with Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How could he do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I thought our friendship meant something to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I thought he had changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.60,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Tirek has stolen enough magic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.85,Celestia,,0,0,0,,that he now has the strength to steal flight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:36.50,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Without pegasi to control the weather
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.69,Celestia,,0,0,0,,there will be no rain in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.80,Celestia,,0,0,0,,There's word he has gone after earth ponies as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:49.31,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Without their strength they will not be able to tend the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:54.67,Luna,,0,0,0,,Ponies will no longer be in control of their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.19,Luna,,0,0,0,,That power will belong solely to Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:00.91,Celestia,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that Tirek is after alicorn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:05.42,Celestia,,0,0,0,,With Discord by his side we will not be able to stop him from taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:09.25,Luna,,0,0,0,,Once it is in his posession, his power will know no bounds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:11.41,Luna,,0,0,0,,and all hope will be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But there is one solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.59,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It is only by making this sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:21.20,Celestia,,0,0,0,,that Equestria and the lands beyond it might be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.90,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We must rid ourselves of our magic
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.86,Celestia,,0,0,0,,before Tirek has the chance to steal it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.29,Somepony,,0,0,0,,To be continued…
